      ],
      "source": "https://www.livingplaces.com/CT/Fairfield_County/Westport_Town/Compo-Owenoke_Historic_District.html"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The Compo–Owenoke Historic District features Colonial Revival, Bungalow, and Tudor Revival homes, with exposed rafters and steep gables.",
