        2
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.westportct.gov/about"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Compo Beach houses were built as seasonal cottages, wood‑framed with shingled walls and open porches.",
